97
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:22,810
Haha!

98
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,180
Jom, Haha!

99
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:27,120
Gosh, berhenti!

100
00:02:25,650 --> 00:02:27,350
(Ini Jeon So Bal.)

101
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,850
- Awak sepatutnya berada di sini. - Jadi Bal.

102
