106
00:02:32,490 --> 00:02:35,560
(Senang berjumpa dengan awak, So Bal!)

107
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:35,860
Itu bagus.

108
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,530
Jadi Bal di sini lagi.

109
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:39,130
- Hello. - Jeon So Bal.

110
00:02:39,130 --> 00:02:40,830
Terima kasih banyak kerana membawa saya ke sini.

111
00:02:40,830 --> 00:02:43,600
Kami ada So Bal dan Kyung Nam di sini hari ini.

112
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,270
Kyung Nam kembali selepas tujuh tahun.

113
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,440
(Kyung Nam kembali ke Running Man selepas 7 tahun.)

114
00:02:45,270 --> 00:02:46,370
